Detailed Description

cvmx_usbc::_hcintmsk#

Host Channel-n Interrupt Mask Register (HCINTMSKn)

This register reflects the mask for each channel status described in the previous section. Mask interrupt: 1'b0 Unmask interrupt: 1'b1
